{"word":"H1986 - הָלַם - hâlam - haw-lam' - Beat","slug":"H1986","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">הָלַם</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Transliteration: </strong>hâlam"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Phonetic: </strong>haw-lam'"},{"paragraph":"<strong>Short Definition: </strong>Beat"},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>&#x05D4;&#x05DC;&#x05DD; - ha&#x0302;lam</b> - <i>haw-lam'</i><p/>A primitive root; to <i>strike</i> down; by implication to <i>hammer</i>, <i>stamp</i>, <i>conquer</i>, <i>disband: - </i>beat (down), break (down), overcome, smite (with the hammer)."},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<strong>Cognate:</strong> <a href=\"#/H1987\">H1987</a>, <a href=\"#/H1989\">H1989</a>, <a href=\"#/H3095\">H3095</a>, <a href=\"#/H4112\">H4112</a>"}]}